OL,3,CMirror to pay Harry 'substantial sum'
OL,4,Cas hacking claims settled
OL,6,FDuke of Sussex's barrister said Mirror
OL,7,FGroup Newspapers will pay Harry "a
OL,8,Fsubstantial additional sum by way of
OL,9,Fdamages" as well as his legal costs,
OL,10,FITV News Correspondent Neil Connery
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThe Duke of Sussex has settled for a
OL,14,F"substantial sum" in the remaining
OL,15,Fparts of his phone hacking claim
OL,16,Fagainst the publisher of the Daily
OL,17,FMirror, the High Court has heard.
