OL,3,CMirror to pay Harry 'substantial sum'
OL,4,Cas hacking claims settled
OL,6,FIn December, the High Court ruled to
OL,7,Faward #140,600 in damages to the Duke
OL,8,Fof Sussex after a trial found his
OL,9,Fmobile was hacked by Group Newspapers
OL,10,F(MGN) journalists between 2006-2011.
OL,12,FThe judge ruled the media group -
OL,13,Fwhich includes The Daily and Sunday
OL,14,FMirror and Sunday People - had been
OL,15,Finvolved in "extensive" phone hacking
OL,16,Ftechniques on a "widespread and
OL,17,Fhabitual basis".
