OL,4,Cas hacking claims settled
OL,6,FDuring a hearing in London on Friday,
OL,7,Fhis barrister David Sherborne
OL,8,Fconfirmed a settlement had been
OL,9,Freached between the duke and MGN.
OL,11,FHe said Mirror Group Newspapers will
OL,12,Fpay Harry "a substantial additional
OL,13,Fsum by way of damages" as well as his
OL,14,Flegal costs.
