OL,3,CMirror to pay Harry 'substantial sum'
OL,4,Cas hacking claims settled
OL,6,FSpeaking outside the court, Mr
OL,7,FSherbone read a statement on behalf of
OL,8,FPrince Harry and said: "Everything we
OL,9,Fsaid was happening at Mirror Group was
OL,10,Fin fact happening, and indeed far
OL,11,Fworse as the Court ruled in its
OL,12,Fextremely damning judgement."
OL,14,FHe added that the case had "uncovered
OL,15,Fand proved the shockingly dishonest"
OL,16,Fpractices from MGN and how it "sought
OL,17,Fto conceal the truth."
