OL,4,Cas hacking claims settled
OL,6,FIt claimed that Piers Morgan, who had
OL,7,Fa stint as editor across the years
OL,8,Fthat the articles were published,
OL,9,F"knew perfectly well what was going
OL,10,Fon."
OL,12,F"His contempt for the Court's ruling
OL,13,Fand his continued attacks ever since
OL,14,Fdemonstrate why it was so important to
OL,15,Fobtain a clear and detailed judgment."
OL,17,FIn December, Mr Morgan delivered a
OL,18,Fscathing speech outside his London
OL,19,Fhome, alleging that Prince Harry
OL,20,F"wouldn't know the truth if it slapped
OL,21,Fhim around his California-tanned face."
