OL,3,CMirror to pay Harry 'substantial sum'
OL,4,Cas hacking claims settled
OL,6,FMr Morgan denies claims he knew about
OL,7,Fthe phone-hacking.
OL,9,FAn MGN spokesperson said: "We are
OL,10,Fpleased to have reached this
OL,11,Fagreement, which gives our business
OL,12,Ffurther clarity to move forward from
OL,13,Fevents that took place many years ago
OL,14,Fand for which we have apologised."
OL,16,FMr Sherborne said the publisher would
OL,17,Fmake an interim payment towards the
OL,18,Fcosts of #400,000.
