OL,6,FA total of 33 articles in Harry's
OL,7,Fclaim were examined during the trial
OL,8,Flast year, with 15 articles found to
OL,9,Fhave been the product of unlawful
OL,10,Finformation gathering.
OL,12,FMr Justice Fancourt concluded that
OL,13,FHarry's phone was hacked "to a modest
OL,14,Fextent" by MGN, awarding him #140,600
OL,15,Fin damages.
OL,17,FBut there were a further 115 articles
OL,18,Fwere in his claim, which may have been
OL,19,Fthe subject of a further trial.
