OL,6,FPrince Harry's claim was that MGN
OL,7,Fjournalists were linked to methods
OL,8,Fincluding phone hacking, so-called
OL,9,F"blagging", or gaining information by
OL,10,Fdeception, and use of private
OL,11,Finvestigators for unlawful activities.
OL,13,FHarry, 39, became the first senior
OL,14,FBritish royal to give evidence in 130
OL,15,Fyears, when he became involved in
OL,16,Fincluding similar claims brought
OL,17,Fagainst Associated Newspapers Limited
OL,18,F(ANL) and News Group Newspapers (NGN).
